            "title": "Educa\u00e7\u00e3o profissional no Brasil do s\u00e9culo XXI : pol\u00edticas, cr\u00edticas e perspectivas - Vol. 1",
            "abstract": [
                "Structural unemployment and criminal management of the pandemic opened up the Brazilian tragedy. Hunger and misery, a drop in family income, difficulty finding a job are once again part of the barbaric daily life of the working class. If it is true that the professional education systems allow a better quality education for a portion of the working class, another portion attend public schools of poor quality, without minimum conditions for carrying out educational work. The chapters in this book seek to show the small achievements, limits and contradictions of the professional education policy, especially in the states of the Brazilian federation",
                "O desemprego estrutural e a gest\u00e3o criminosa da pandemia escancararam a trag\u00e9dia brasileira. Fome e mis\u00e9ria, queda na renda familiar, dificuldade de arranjar emprego mais uma vez fazem parte do cotidiano b\u00e1rbaro da classe trabalhadora. Se \u00e9 verdade que os sistemas de educa\u00e7\u00e3o profissional permitem uma educa\u00e7\u00e3o de melhor qualidade para uma parcela da classe trabalhadora, outra parcela frequenta escolas p\u00fablicas de p\u00e9ssima qualidade, sem condi\u00e7\u00f5es m\u00ednimas para a realiza\u00e7\u00e3o do trabalho educacional. Os cap\u00edtulos deste livro procuram mostrar as pequenas conquistas, os limites e as contradi\u00e7\u00f5es da pol\u00edtica de educa\u00e7\u00e3o profissional, especialmente nos Estados da federa\u00e7\u00e3o brasileira"
            ],
